  "title": "Savory Dense Jamaican Polish Sausage Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and comforting stew featuring Polish sausage and Jamaican spices, perfect for a cold evening. This dish is packed with umami flavor and dense with tender sausage and vegetables.",
